@startuml SME_Ops_Sequence_AI_Insights
title UC23 — View AI business insights — §2.3.7

actor Owner
participant "Dashboard UI" as Web
participant "AiController" as API
participant "AiService" as Svc
participant "DashboardService" as Dash
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Owner -> Web : load insights panel
Web -> API : GET /ai/insights?days=30
API -> Svc : getInsights(orgId, days)
Svc -> Dash : fetch summary & trends
Dash -> DB : query sales, stock, expenses
DB --> Dash : aggregates
Dash --> Svc : metrics
Svc --> Svc : build rule-based cards
Svc --> API : insight cards[]
API --> Web : JSON
Web --> Owner : display insights

note right of Svc
  No OpenRouter required (FR-17)
end note

@enduml
